{"lemma":"حاصِل","slug":"حاصِل","root":"ح.ص.ل","root_slug":"ح-ص-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ص-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8256"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%B5%D9%90%D9%84"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"conclusion, outcome, yield, result, bottom line, quotient, sum, product"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"depot, storage, depository, department"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"active participle of حَصَلَ (ḥaṣala)","tags":["active","form-of","participle"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of حَصَلَ (ḥaṣala)."},"ipa":["/ħaː.sˤil/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8256","headword_ar":"حَاصِلٌ","root":"HSl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, Msb, K, KL) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSiylapN","text_ar":"حَصِيلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K &c.) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHoSuwlN","text_ar":"مَحْصُولٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) [and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHaS~alN","text_ar":"مُحَصَّلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Produce;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is produced, educed, extracted, taken forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fetched out: what is made apparent: profit, advantage, gain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acquisition:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL in explanation of the first word [but applying to all]:) [the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"result"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing:]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a remain, remainder, remaining portion, remnant, relic, residue,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remains,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what remains, and continues,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when the rest has gone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passed away:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) it is of a reckoning, or computation, and of actions, and the like: (T, M, TA:) pl. of the second"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSaAy^ilu","text_ar":"حَصَايِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA.) The first also particularly signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is cleared,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"purified,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of silver [and of gold]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the stone of the mine."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"produce,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"net produce,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of land &c.; of anything that is a source of revenue; as also the third. The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"result"},{"kind":"text","text":"of an arithmetical process; the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sum,"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"product,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quotient."},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sum,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sum and substance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"essential import,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a sentence or the like; as also the third (see 2) and the fourth. And the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"result, end, conclusion, event, issue, ultimate consequence"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"effect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ultimity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything.]       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawoSalapN","text_ar":"حَوْصَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","Msb","K","KL","TA"]}]}}